typeProperties.script:
source(output(
		{日コード} as string,
		{日} as string,
		{月コード} as string,
		{月} as string,
		{四半期コード} as string,
		{四半期} as string,
		{半期コード} as string,
		{半期} as string,
		{年度コード} as string,
		{年度} as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	ignoreNoFilesFound: false) ~> source1
source1 sink(allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	deletable:false,
	insertable:true,
	updateable:false,
	upsertable:false,
	format: 'table',
	staged: true,
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true,
	errorHandlingOption: 'stopOnFirstError') ~> sink1
